government can't reroute the freight <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">train</ENAMEX> in a better direction, it's hard to
see how it can derail it. The metaphor undermines the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Losing Ground</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Murray</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">guy</ENAMEX> who writes that "[<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">u</ENAMEX>]ntil the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">government</ENAMEX> began masking the
